### Flow 3: Last-Minute Mobile Booking (45 seconds)
1. **Open app** (1s): Recently viewed shows
2. **Tap "This Weekend"** (2s): Quick filter
3. **Tap first event** (3s): Looks good
4. **Tap "Quick Book"** (2s): Skip details page
5. **1 ticket selected** (1s): Default quantity
